    Compute velocity for x, y, and its amplited

    compute_velocity_table.Rd

    Compute velocity for x, y, and its amplited

    compute_velocity_table(x, y, trial, sample_rate, velocity_time_window)

    Arguments

    x

    vector with x coordinates in degrees of visual angle

    y

    vector with y coordinates in degrees of visual angle

    trial

    vector with trial index

    sample_rate

    sample rate in Hz

    velocity_time_window

    Time window for velocity computation in milliseconds

    Value

    data.frame with columns x, y, and amp

    Examples

    compute_velocity_table(rnorm(1000), rnorm(1000), rep(1, 1000), 250, 20)
